WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:12.887 --> 00:00:14.806
Itadori. why is his nose bleeding?

2
00:00:14.889 --> 00:00:15.724
What?

3
00:00:15.807 --> 00:00:16.683
I punched him.

4
00:00:16.766 --> 00:00:19.185
-When?
-At the very start.

5
00:00:19.269 --> 00:00:21.187
Did he touch you with his hand?

6
00:00:21.271 --> 00:00:22.188
Yes.

7
00:00:23.481 --> 00:00:26.192
My attacks have zero effect on him.

8
00:00:26.276 --> 00:00:28.111
What?

9
00:00:28.194 --> 00:00:30.572
-Why?
-The reason will come during the lecture.

10
00:00:30.655 --> 00:00:34.576
First. he may not be able
to use his ability on Itadori.

11
00:00:34.659 --> 00:00:38.121
Second. he has a reason
not to kill Itadori.

12
00:00:38.204 --> 00:00:40.248
Either way. it's an advantage.

13
00:00:40.749 --> 00:00:43.710
But I can stifle his movements.

14
00:00:45.378 --> 00:00:49.424
Let's create openings for each other
and take the opportunity to attack.

15
00:00:50.508 --> 00:00:52.927
We must exorcise him here.

16
00:00:55.180 --> 00:00:56.306
Okay!

17
00:01:03.605 --> 00:01:06.399
Be mindful of Yuji Itadori…

18
00:01:07.317 --> 00:01:10.528
and get rid of 7:3 Sorcerer first.

19
00:01:31.424 --> 00:01:34.093
I thought this was good.

20
00:01:34.177 --> 00:01:36.638
But they evaded my attacks.

21
00:01:36.721 --> 00:01:40.016
After they dodge it.
the tips of my needles will come off.

22
00:01:40.099 --> 00:01:41.851
It's only good for small fries.

23
00:01:42.352 --> 00:01:43.311
Let's stop this.

24
00:01:54.072 --> 00:01:56.157
Before he changes his shape…

25
00:01:56.241 --> 00:01:58.493
-He charges his cursed energy first!
-Very good.

26
00:02:00.245 --> 00:02:02.413
Even if I make myself smaller.

27
00:02:02.497 --> 00:02:05.708
I still risk getting killed
by Yuji Itadori in one blow.

28
00:02:05.792 --> 00:02:08.086
He's really my nemesis.

29
00:02:08.169 --> 00:02:10.630
Let's make him behave nicely.

30
00:02:12.507 --> 00:02:14.175
Transfigured humans.

31
00:02:14.759 --> 00:02:16.678
He still has some stored.

32
00:02:17.178 --> 00:02:19.013
Kill that short-haired brat.

33
00:02:27.397 --> 00:02:29.482
I knew it.

34
00:02:29.566 --> 00:02:31.609
That kid can't kill humans.

35
00:02:46.457 --> 00:02:48.960
Let's play…

36
00:02:57.385 --> 00:02:59.012
Please…

37
00:02:59.637 --> 00:03:01.472
Kill me…

38
00:03:05.894 --> 00:03:08.563
I want you to fight against him next.

39
00:03:08.646 --> 00:03:10.398
Will he cry this time?

40
00:03:10.481 --> 00:03:14.360
He's a foolish brat
who can't match ideal with reality.

41
00:03:14.444 --> 00:03:16.362
That's not true.

42
00:03:16.446 --> 00:03:19.949
He's on it right now.

43
00:03:20.033 --> 00:03:21.868
If anything.

44
00:03:21.951 --> 00:03:23.620
you're the foolish one.

45
00:03:30.293 --> 00:03:31.961
You killed them?

46
00:03:34.964 --> 00:03:36.883
His cursed energy level increased.

47
00:03:37.425 --> 00:03:39.719
I'll change my shape
right before the impact--

48
00:03:51.147 --> 00:03:53.775
There's no time for me
to make a substitute.

49
00:03:54.275 --> 00:03:56.110
What…

50
00:03:56.194 --> 00:03:59.280
What a fresh inspiration!

51
00:03:59.822 --> 00:04:01.032
Is this…

52
00:04:01.991 --> 00:04:03.201
death?

53
00:04:11.042 --> 00:04:12.835
I can do it now. right?

54
00:04:19.634 --> 00:04:21.552
Domain Expansion.

55
00:04:37.610 --> 00:04:39.821
Self-Embodiment of Perfection!

56
00:04:41.406 --> 00:04:42.699
Darn it.

57
00:04:44.701 --> 00:04:46.119
Now…

58
00:04:48.288 --> 00:04:50.039
I just want to thank you.

59
00:06:26.469 --> 00:06:27.637
Are you serious?

60
00:06:30.306 --> 00:06:32.809
Why was only Nanamin trapped inside?

61
00:06:32.892 --> 00:06:34.352
If this goes on…

62
00:06:34.435 --> 00:06:35.686
If this goes on…

63
00:06:40.191 --> 00:06:42.068
Domain Expansion.

64
00:06:42.151 --> 00:06:45.363
An enclosed space constructed
using cursed energy.

65
00:06:45.446 --> 00:06:49.367
A secret weapon that will enhance
the owner's strengths.

66
00:06:49.867 --> 00:06:53.496
It's the pinnacle of cursed techniques
that I couldn't reach.

67
00:06:54.455 --> 00:06:58.292
To use any cursed technique
which transfigures the soul.

68
00:06:58.376 --> 00:07:01.754
he probably needs to touch someone
with the palm of his original hand.

69
00:07:01.838 --> 00:07:05.049
But now that I'm inside his domain…

70
00:07:05.133 --> 00:07:10.096
I'm literally in the palm
of my opponent's hand.

71
00:07:11.639 --> 00:07:12.598
Darn it.

72
00:07:12.682 --> 00:07:15.143
Jujutsu Sorcerers are shit.

73
00:07:15.226 --> 00:07:18.187
Sometimes. we have to force our comrades

74
00:07:18.271 --> 00:07:21.107
to accept and sacrifice
their lives for others.

75
00:07:21.190 --> 00:07:22.942
That's why I quit.

76
00:07:23.943 --> 00:07:25.695
Or rather. I escaped.

77
00:07:27.572 --> 00:07:29.615
Do you like baguette sandwiches?

78
00:07:29.699 --> 00:07:30.533
What?

79
00:07:31.200 --> 00:07:32.160
What?

80
00:07:32.910 --> 00:07:35.288
You always buy this. right?

81
00:07:35.371 --> 00:07:37.248
Well. yes.

82
00:07:37.331 --> 00:07:40.042
The nearby convenience store
no longer sells it.

83
00:07:40.126 --> 00:07:42.753
Our bread's better than those
in convenience stores. right?

84
00:07:42.837 --> 00:07:45.256
I mean. this is a bakery.

85
00:07:45.339 --> 00:07:47.383
You're so mean.

86
00:07:48.926 --> 00:07:50.887
Please come again!

87
00:07:53.806 --> 00:07:55.016
A Fly Head.

88
00:07:56.559 --> 00:07:59.020
I guess it's fine to leave it alone.

89
00:08:00.021 --> 00:08:01.772
It will be trouble if I do a bad job

90
00:08:01.856 --> 00:08:03.649
and she thinks I'm some shady medium.

91
00:08:10.323 --> 00:08:12.283
How is it going?

92
00:08:12.366 --> 00:08:16.537
Giving us money
means giving us their lives.

93
00:08:16.621 --> 00:08:20.208
I don't need to talk much about
how to balance the benefits and risks.

94
00:08:20.291 --> 00:08:23.878
No need to do anything special
at the beginning.

95
00:08:23.961 --> 00:08:26.714
You just have to
face the clients sincerely.

96
00:08:26.797 --> 00:08:28.674
Don't forget this.

97
00:08:28.758 --> 00:08:29.926
Yes!

98
00:08:30.426 --> 00:08:31.928
Nanami.

99
00:08:32.011 --> 00:08:34.555
Don't make it sound so rigid.

100
00:08:34.639 --> 00:08:36.140
You'll scare the newbie.

101
00:08:36.641 --> 00:08:40.603
Newbie. your top priority
is the company's profit.

102
00:08:40.686 --> 00:08:43.439
This will also be our clients' benefits.

103
00:08:43.523 --> 00:08:47.109
Even persuading clients
to buy stocks that won't rise?

104
00:08:48.569 --> 00:08:52.990
This is the legitimate reward for us
who watch the market 24 hours a day.

105
00:08:53.074 --> 00:08:55.201
Isn't this your second year. Nanami?

106
00:08:55.284 --> 00:08:57.870
You're clever. You should let loose.

107
00:08:57.954 --> 00:08:59.413
I have high expectations of you.

108
00:09:00.373 --> 00:09:01.791
I'm a person

109
00:09:01.874 --> 00:09:03.834
who does not have a concept of

110
00:09:03.918 --> 00:09:06.170
what is worth doing.
and what is worth living for.

111
00:09:06.254 --> 00:09:09.632
I'll just earn some money
until I'm 30 or 40 years old.

112
00:09:10.132 --> 00:09:13.719
then I'll enjoy an aimless life
in a country with low cost of living.

113
00:09:14.595 --> 00:09:16.430
Four years after graduation.

114
00:09:16.514 --> 00:09:19.976
I think about money all the time.

115
00:09:20.685 --> 00:09:22.186
Curse or other human beings.

116
00:09:22.270 --> 00:09:24.564
I can stay away from them if I have money.

117
00:09:25.565 --> 00:09:26.440
Money.

118
00:09:27.066 --> 00:09:28.484
Money.

119
00:09:28.568 --> 00:09:29.944
Money.

120
00:09:31.028 --> 00:09:32.863
Money.

121
00:09:33.447 --> 00:09:35.157
As long as I have money.

122
00:09:36.367 --> 00:09:37.785
Are you okay?

123
00:09:38.369 --> 00:09:39.829
Have you been sleeping well?

124
00:09:40.830 --> 00:09:44.750
What about you? You look tired.

125
00:09:45.668 --> 00:09:47.211
You can tell?

126
00:09:47.795 --> 00:09:50.673
I feel that my shoulders
are quite heavy recently.

127
00:09:50.756 --> 00:09:52.883
Besides. I don't sleep well too.

128
00:09:54.218 --> 00:09:59.390
My job is to
let the rich entrust their money to me

129
00:10:00.016 --> 00:10:02.643
and make them richer.

130
00:10:02.727 --> 00:10:04.395
Something like that.

131
00:10:04.478 --> 00:10:07.940
To be honest.
no one will be sad even if I'm gone.

132
00:10:08.024 --> 00:10:11.485
But if the bakery is gone.
people who want to eat bread will be sad.

133
00:10:11.986 --> 00:10:16.240
But somehow. a job like mine
that's outside of such a human cycle

134
00:10:16.324 --> 00:10:19.869
gives me a better salary.

135
00:10:19.952 --> 00:10:22.913
It's quite strange when I think about it.

136
00:10:24.415 --> 00:10:27.084
-Are you showing off?
-No.

137
00:10:28.461 --> 00:10:31.505
I'm sorry.
It's quite hard for me to understand.

138
00:10:32.923 --> 00:10:35.092
Can you come forward a little?

139
00:10:35.885 --> 00:10:36.719
What?

140
00:10:40.348 --> 00:10:42.475
-What?
-How do you feel now?

141
00:10:42.558 --> 00:10:44.518
What? Let me see.

142
00:10:45.061 --> 00:10:46.729
What? It feels light!

143
00:10:46.812 --> 00:10:49.440
Go to the hospital if you still feel sick.

144
00:10:49.523 --> 00:10:50.941
I'll get going now.

145
00:10:52.151 --> 00:10:53.361
Oh. my!

146
00:10:53.444 --> 00:10:55.321
Wait!

147
00:10:55.404 --> 00:10:56.572
Wait!

148
00:10:56.656 --> 00:10:57.907
Excuse me.

149
00:11:00.117 --> 00:11:01.869
Thank you!

150
00:11:02.745 --> 00:11:04.789
Please come again!

151
00:11:04.872 --> 00:11:08.042
-"Thank you."
-Strange. Did he not hear me?

152
00:11:08.125 --> 00:11:09.502
Thank you!

153
00:11:09.585 --> 00:11:12.046
Please come again!

154
00:11:12.129 --> 00:11:16.842
I thought I had nothing to live for.

155
00:11:16.926 --> 00:11:17.760
SATORU GOJO

156
00:11:18.511 --> 00:11:20.638
Hello. It's Nanami.

157
00:11:20.721 --> 00:11:22.181
I would like to talk to you.

158
00:11:22.890 --> 00:11:23.766
Yes.

159
00:11:23.849 --> 00:11:25.935
I'll return to Jujutsu High tomorrow…

160
00:11:26.602 --> 00:11:28.187
Why are you laughing?

161
00:11:32.566 --> 00:11:33.901
Idle Transfiguration.

162
00:11:34.860 --> 00:11:36.237
I thank you.

163
00:11:40.908 --> 00:11:42.493
No need.

164
00:11:48.541 --> 00:11:51.502
I've received enough gratitude.

165
00:11:52.837 --> 00:11:54.255
I have no regrets.

166
00:12:09.061 --> 00:12:10.521
How did he enter?

167
00:12:11.730 --> 00:12:12.982
I see.

168
00:12:13.065 --> 00:12:15.651
The greater the barrier.

169
00:12:15.734 --> 00:12:18.070
the weaker it is to external attacks.

170
00:12:18.154 --> 00:12:21.740
Domain is only focused on closing.

171
00:12:22.241 --> 00:12:24.743
In other words.
it's easy for an invasion to happen.

172
00:12:25.494 --> 00:12:28.956
Because it brings no benefit
to the intruder.

173
00:12:30.458 --> 00:12:33.711
Even more so for the Unlimited Void
and Self-Embodiment of Perfection.

174
00:12:34.211 --> 00:12:39.216
whereby victory is confirmed
when the opponent is trapped inside.

175
00:12:41.218 --> 00:12:42.136
However.

176
00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:44.680
Itadori is an exception.

177
00:12:45.181 --> 00:12:47.892
There's something in him
that cannot be touched!

178
00:12:52.980 --> 00:12:54.565
I told you.

179
00:12:57.651 --> 00:12:59.820
No second chances.

180
00:13:05.159 --> 00:13:08.120
Everyone on earth
and in heaven must listen to him.

181
00:13:08.662 --> 00:13:12.583
He acts solely based on his mood.

182
00:13:13.167 --> 00:13:15.085
It's either you die…

183
00:13:15.753 --> 00:13:17.588
or I die.

184
00:13:18.214 --> 00:13:19.548
It doesn't matter.

185
00:13:20.841 --> 00:13:22.885
Except for that guy.

186
00:13:23.886 --> 00:13:26.805
I couldn't care less.

187
00:14:03.300 --> 00:14:05.469
What happened?

188
00:14:12.393 --> 00:14:14.311
I'll kill you!

189
00:14:14.395 --> 00:14:18.023
Domain Expansion has used up
too much cursed energy.

190
00:14:18.107 --> 00:14:20.943
It was my last resort.

191
00:14:21.026 --> 00:14:22.319
But that scoundrel. Sukuna…

192
00:14:22.403 --> 00:14:25.072
But this is the critical moment!

193
00:14:25.155 --> 00:14:26.949
Squeeze it out!

194
00:14:27.032 --> 00:14:28.659
The last of my cursed energy!

195
00:14:32.288 --> 00:14:33.831
The target is large.

196
00:14:34.331 --> 00:14:36.709
The flow of his cursed energy
is slowing down.

197
00:14:36.792 --> 00:14:38.460
There will be no counterattack.

198
00:14:39.044 --> 00:14:41.171
I can definitely attack him.

199
00:14:41.255 --> 00:14:42.923
It's my last chance.

200
00:14:45.217 --> 00:14:47.553
No need for tricks.

201
00:14:53.058 --> 00:14:54.727
Divergent Fist!

202
00:15:04.445 --> 00:15:06.488
What's going on?

203
00:15:06.572 --> 00:15:08.365
I felt nothing.

204
00:15:12.453 --> 00:15:15.956
-Wait!
-It was fun.

205
00:15:22.713 --> 00:15:26.300
Ino. the target has
escaped into the sewers.

206
00:15:27.092 --> 00:15:27.927
That's right.

207
00:15:28.510 --> 00:15:32.723
Please conduct a thorough search
of the direction southeast to my location.

208
00:15:32.806 --> 00:15:34.683
You should be able to exorcise him.

209
00:15:35.351 --> 00:15:37.186
We're going after him too!

210
00:15:38.687 --> 00:15:40.064
Itadori!

211
00:15:40.147 --> 00:15:41.941
Move. my body!

212
00:15:42.024 --> 00:15:44.568
Weren't you going to kill him?

213
00:15:45.152 --> 00:15:49.406
-I must crush him…
-Itadori!

214
00:15:49.490 --> 00:15:50.574
Itadori!

215
00:16:13.055 --> 00:16:14.723
That's the King of Curses.

216
00:16:14.807 --> 00:16:16.517
Ryomen Sukuna.

217
00:16:17.142 --> 00:16:21.105
His current cursed energy
is inferior to Jogo.

218
00:16:21.605 --> 00:16:22.731
However.

219
00:16:22.815 --> 00:16:24.817
his presence…

220
00:16:24.900 --> 00:16:27.236
His soul is on
a completely different level.

221
00:16:27.820 --> 00:16:29.738
I'm certain now.

222
00:16:29.822 --> 00:16:31.865
Even if we were wiped out.

223
00:16:31.949 --> 00:16:35.661
the era of curses can begin
as long as Sukuna is resurrected.

224
00:16:36.245 --> 00:16:38.747
But it's so troublesome.

225
00:16:38.831 --> 00:16:45.004
I really want to kill Yuji Itadori now!

226
00:16:48.799 --> 00:16:51.844
I'm feeling so impatient!

227
00:16:51.927 --> 00:16:53.804
But forget it.

228
00:16:53.887 --> 00:16:58.142
Unlike the body.
the soul can be killed many times.

229
00:16:59.977 --> 00:17:03.147
How should I kill him next time?

230
00:17:07.192 --> 00:17:09.570
Didn't I tell you to rest?

231
00:17:10.821 --> 00:17:12.197
Are you lecturing me?

232
00:17:12.781 --> 00:17:16.994
No lecturing needed for my savior.

233
00:17:17.745 --> 00:17:18.704
Me?

234
00:17:18.787 --> 00:17:23.000
Mahito's cursed techniques
can interfere with other people's souls.

235
00:17:23.500 --> 00:17:28.464
You made him touch Sukuna's soul
when you invaded his domain.

236
00:17:29.256 --> 00:17:30.924
Thanks to you. I'm saved.

237
00:17:32.301 --> 00:17:35.304
But I didn't switch.

238
00:17:36.430 --> 00:17:38.390
Sukuna didn't come out.

239
00:17:38.474 --> 00:17:40.684
Instead. Mahito went in.

240
00:17:41.769 --> 00:17:44.480
Then I wasn't the one who saved you.

241
00:17:44.563 --> 00:17:46.440
Sukuna did it on a whim.

242
00:17:47.232 --> 00:17:50.694
Nanami. I killed humans today.

243
00:17:51.779 --> 00:17:54.198
People will die. It's inevitable.

244
00:17:54.281 --> 00:17:56.825
But I want their deaths
to be justified. at least.

245
00:17:57.367 --> 00:17:59.119
That was what I was thinking.

246
00:17:59.620 --> 00:18:02.664
That's why I only think about
not pulling the trigger.

247
00:18:03.373 --> 00:18:07.711
But now that I pulled the trigger myself.
I don't understand it anymore.

248
00:18:08.504 --> 00:18:10.255
What's the right way to die?

249
00:18:10.339 --> 00:18:12.800
I don't know either.

250
00:18:13.300 --> 00:18:18.555
The good should die peacefully
and the bad should have a horrible death.

251
00:18:18.639 --> 00:18:21.850
but most people are neither good nor evil.

252
00:18:22.351 --> 00:18:26.396
I believe that all deaths
come to all people differently.

253
00:18:26.480 --> 00:18:30.067
and giving proper guidance
to all the souls is just tiring.

254
00:18:30.150 --> 00:18:32.069
I don't recommend you to do that.

255
00:18:33.403 --> 00:18:37.032
Even so. you'll still try to do it.

256
00:18:38.242 --> 00:18:40.327
Just be careful not to die.

257
00:18:40.410 --> 00:18:44.081
If you weren't there today.
I would've died.

258
00:18:44.164 --> 00:18:47.793
People who rely on you
will start to appear…

259
00:18:48.418 --> 00:18:52.339
since you're already
a Jujutsu Sorcerer. Itadori.

260
00:18:57.594 --> 00:19:00.681
Put it in the box when you're done.

261
00:19:00.764 --> 00:19:02.516
You don't need to write your names.

262
00:19:02.599 --> 00:19:04.226
QUESTIONNAIRE ON BULLYING

263
00:19:24.121 --> 00:19:28.625
So it's you who injured Yoshino. Ito.

264
00:19:29.376 --> 00:19:32.671
I don't want to be scolded by the one

265
00:19:32.754 --> 00:19:35.340
who's too afraid to do anything
at that time.

266
00:19:36.175 --> 00:19:38.719
He's quit school and moved away. right?

267
00:19:38.802 --> 00:19:40.262
Can't we forget about it?

268
00:19:41.263 --> 00:19:42.347
By the way.

269
00:19:42.431 --> 00:19:45.601
my left hand can't move since then.

270
00:19:45.684 --> 00:19:48.395
I'm asking about your crime.

271
00:19:48.478 --> 00:19:51.607
Think of that injury
as your punishment and reflect on it.

272
00:19:51.690 --> 00:19:53.358
What about your punishment?

273
00:19:53.442 --> 00:19:55.402
It's coming.

274
00:19:55.485 --> 00:19:58.822
I want to take a good look
at the things I didn't see clearly.

275
00:19:59.948 --> 00:20:02.367
Whether it's me or you…

276
00:20:02.951 --> 00:20:06.955
We'll carry the sin
of ruining Junpei's heart forever.

277
00:20:07.456 --> 00:20:10.375
I'll be watching you. Ito.

278
00:20:16.006 --> 00:20:18.800
I still don't know
the meaning of a justified death.

279
00:20:19.426 --> 00:20:20.469
Then at least…

280
00:20:22.346 --> 00:20:23.305
Before I understand…

281
00:20:27.267 --> 00:20:29.228
Before I kill that guy…

282
00:20:40.030 --> 00:20:41.782
I will never…

283
00:20:44.243 --> 00:20:45.535
lose again.

284
00:22:16.543 --> 00:22:17.919
Juju Stroll.

285
00:22:22.466 --> 00:22:23.884
Can we eat now?

286
00:22:23.967 --> 00:22:24.968
Salmon.

287
00:22:32.142 --> 00:22:33.852
This meatball is delicious.

288
00:22:33.935 --> 00:22:34.811
Who made it?

289
00:22:34.895 --> 00:22:36.563
It's me.

290
00:22:36.646 --> 00:22:38.231
You can make it easily.

291
00:22:38.315 --> 00:22:41.651
1. PUT IN ALL THE INGREDIENTS
AND USE DOUBLE THE AMOUNT OF GINGER

292
00:22:41.735 --> 00:22:44.946
2. MIX AND KNEAD WELL

293
00:22:45.030 --> 00:22:49.618
3. SHAPE MEATBALLS WITH A SPOON
AND PLACE THEM INTO THE POT

294
00:22:49.701 --> 00:22:52.496
INGREDIENTS: CHICKEN MEAT.
MINCED SPRING ONIONS. GINGER SAUCE

295
00:22:52.579 --> 00:22:54.998
EGG YOLKS (YOU CAN INCLUDE EGG WHITES)
SALT AND PEPPER

296
00:22:55.582 --> 00:22:56.750
Leaf mustard.

297
00:22:57.751 --> 00:23:00.170
So Fushiguro can cook.

298
00:23:00.253 --> 00:23:01.379
I'm not surprised.

299
00:23:02.089 --> 00:23:05.008
No. Itadori taught me how to make it.

300
00:23:15.143 --> 00:23:16.686
I see.

301
00:23:18.271 --> 00:23:20.816
Itadori's posthumous work.

302
00:23:20.899 --> 00:23:22.526
That doesn't sound right.

303
00:23:25.487 --> 00:23:27.614
This meatball is so delicious.

304
00:23:27.697 --> 00:23:28.657
They are.

305
00:23:28.740 --> 00:23:30.408
You can make it really easily.

306
00:23:32.327 --> 00:23:35.413
Fushiguro can make it too
since I taught him.

307
00:23:38.625 --> 00:23:41.294
I want to see them soon.
